### CreateDwcMeasurementInput type:
```ts
type FloraMeasurementFields = {
  dbh?: string;               // cm
  totalHeight?: string;       // meters
  basalDiameter?: string;     // cm
  canopyCoverPercent?: string; // percentage
};

type CreateDwcMeasurementInput = {
  occurrenceRef: string;      // AT-URI to the parent occurrence record (required)
  occurrenceID?: string;      // for cross-system interop
  flora: FloraMeasurementFields;
  measuredBy?: string;
  measurementDate?: string;
  measurementMethod?: string;
  measurementRemarks?: string;
  rkey?: string;
};
```

### Record structure built by the mutation:
```ts
{
  $type: 'app.gainforest.dwc.measurement',
  occurrenceRef: input.occurrenceRef,
  occurrenceID: input.occurrenceID,
  result: {
    $type: 'app.gainforest.dwc.measurement#floraMeasurement',
    ...input.flora,  // only include fields that are defined
  },
  measuredBy: input.measuredBy,
  measurementDate: input.measurementDate,
  measurementMethod: input.measurementMethod,
  measurementRemarks: input.measurementRemarks,
  createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),
}
```

### Key detail: only include flora fields that are defined (not undefined). If a field is undefined, omit it from the result object entirely.

